# BCDel89 Web Components

This is a web component library from BCDel89 that includes the following web-components:

- bcd-rating


## Installation


```bash
npm install --save bcd-web-components
```

## Usage

```html
<bcd-rating rating="3" max="5"></bcd-rating>
```
